## Demo App Structure

- **Root**: `demo-app/` (Next.js App Router)
- **App router**: `demo-app/app/`
  - `layout.tsx`: wraps pages with `ThemeProvider` and `FinaticProvider`
  - `page.tsx`: dashboard landing page
  - `(dashboard)/`: wgroup for sidebar-routed pages
    - Each feature folder has:
      - `page.tsx`: PascalCase default export component named `XxxPage`
      - `_components/`: co-located feature components in PascalCase
  - `providers/`: global providers (e.g., `FinaticProvider.tsx`, `ThemeProvider.tsx`)
  - `api/`: Next.js route handlers for server-side helpers
- **Shared UI**: `demo-app/components/` and `demo-app/components/ui/`
- **Lib**: `demo-app/lib/` for helpers like `cn`

## Navigation & Layout

- Sidebar lives in `demo-app/components/app-sidebar.tsx` and defines routes like `/auth`, `/portal`, `/methods`, `/trading`, `/developer`, `/settings`.
- Pages use a standard layout:
  - Import `AppSidebar` from `@/components/app-sidebar`
  - Render a full-height container with sidebar and a `main` scroll area

```12:35:/workspaces/Finatic/codebases/Frontend/FinaticClientSDK/demo-app/app/layout.tsx
export default function RootLayout({
  children,
}: Readonly<{
  children: React.ReactNode
}>) {
  return (
    <html lang="en" suppressHydrationWarning>
      <body className={`font-sans ${GeistSans.variable} ${GeistMono.variable}`}>
        <Suspense fallback={null}>
          <FinaticProvider>
            <ThemeProvider attribute="class" defaultTheme="system" enableSystem disableTransitionOnChange>
              {children}
            </ThemeProvider>
          </FinaticProvider>
        </Suspense>
        <Analytics />
      </body>
    </html>
  )
}
```

## Import Aliases

- `demo-app/tsconfig.json` defines `@/*` to `./*`. Use absolute imports, never relative.

```21:23:/workspaces/Finatic/codebases/Frontend/FinaticClientSDK/demo-app/tsconfig.json
"paths": {
  "@/*": ["./*"]
}
```

## State & SDK Initialization

- Global Finatic SDK context is provided by `FinaticProvider` with logging, mock mode, usage stats, and fetch instrumentation.

```67:75:/workspaces/Finatic/codebases/Frontend/FinaticClientSDK/demo-app/app/providers/FinaticProvider.tsx
export function FinaticProvider({ children }: { children: React.ReactNode }) {
  const [finatic, setFinatic] = useState<FinaticConnect | null>(null);
  const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false);
  const [error, setError] = useState<string | null>(null);
  const [isMockMode, setIsMockMode] = useState(false);
  const [sessionInfo, setSessionInfo] = useState<string>('Not initialized');
  const [logs, setLogs] = useState<LogEntry[]>([]);
```

## Page Pattern

- Page files export a default component named `XxxPage` and compose feature components from `_components`.

```1:13:/workspaces/Finatic/codebases/Frontend/FinaticClientSDK/demo-app/app/(dashboard)/auth/page.tsx
import { AppSidebar } from "@/components/app-sidebar"
import { AuthenticationPortal } from "@/app/(dashboard)/auth/_components/AuthenticationPage"

export default function AuthPage() {
  return (
    <div className="flex h-screen bg-background">
      <AppSidebar />
      <main className="flex-1 overflow-auto">
        <AuthenticationPortal />
      </main>
    </div>
  )
}
```

